background-phi-colors.spaceBaseColor.des: Space background colors are automatically generated by rotating the hue by 1 / phi all around based on this color. If this value is null `background-phi-colors.baseColor` will be used instead.
background-phi-colors.symbolBaseColor.de: Symbol background colors are automatically generated by rotating the hue by 1 / phi all around based on this color. If this value is null `background-phi-colors.baseColor` will be used instead.
background-phi-colors.symbolColorMap.des: You can specify the background color for each symbol.
background-phi-colors.tokenBaseColor.des: Token background colors are automatically generated by rotating the hue by 1 / phi all around based on this color. If this value is null `background-phi-colors.baseColor` will be used instead.
background-phi-colors.tokenColorMap.desc: You can specify the background color for each token.
background-phi-colors.indentMode.descrip: `none`: does not color indents, `light`: colors indents statically, `smart`: colors the current indent, `full`: light + smart,
